theorem Topology.closure_interior_compl_eq_compl_interior_closure
    {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A : Set X} :
    closure (interior (Aᶜ)) = (interior (closure A))ᶜ := by
  classical
  -- First, identify the complements of the two sets we want to compare.
  have h_compl : (closure (interior (Aᶜ)))ᶜ = interior (closure A) := by
    -- Apply the complement/interior relationship to `interior (Aᶜ)`.
    have h₁ :=
      (Topology.interior_compl_eq_compl_closure
        (X := X) (A := interior (Aᶜ))).symm
    -- Rewrite `closure A` in terms of `interior (Aᶜ)`.
    have h_cl :
        closure A = (interior (Aᶜ))ᶜ := by
      have h :=
        Topology.closure_compl_eq_compl_interior (X := X) (A := Aᶜ)
      simpa [Set.compl_compl] using h
    simpa [h_cl] using h₁
  -- Take complements of both sides of the previous equality.
  have h := congrArg (fun s : Set X => sᶜ) h_compl
  simpa [Set.compl_compl] using h

theorem Set.compl_compl {α : Type*} (s : Set α) : sᶜᶜ = (s : Set α) := by
  classical
  ext x
  by_cases hx : x ∈ s
  · simp [hx]
  · simp [hx]

theorem Topology.P1_mono {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A B : Set X}
    (hAB : A ⊆ B) :
    Topology.P1 B → Topology.P1 A := by
  intro hP1B
  dsimp [Topology.P1] at *
  intro x hxA
  have hxB : x ∈ B := hAB hxA
  have hxClB : x ∈ closure (interior B) := hP1B hxB
  have h_subset : closure (interior B) ⊆ closure (interior A) := by
    have h_int : interior B ⊆ interior A := interior_mono hAB
    exact closure_mono h_int
  exact h_subset hxClB

theorem Topology.interior_closure_interior_mono
    {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A B : Set X} (hAB : A ⊆ B) :
    interior (closure (interior A)) ⊆ interior (closure (interior B)) := by
  exact interior_mono (closure_mono (interior_mono hAB))

theorem Topology.interior_inter_closure_compl_eq_empty
    {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] (A : Set X) :
    interior A ∩ closure (Aᶜ) = (∅ : Set X) := by
  have h : closure (Aᶜ : Set X) = (interior A)ᶜ :=
    Topology.closure_compl_eq_compl_interior (X := X) (A := A)
  calc
    interior A ∩ closure (Aᶜ) =
        interior A ∩ (interior A)ᶜ := by
          simpa [h]
    _ = (∅ : Set X) := by
          simpa [Set.inter_compl_self]
